// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-3146 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 22b05ffc-99b0-56b1-bbd3-bda117afe75c

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*")
